#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/properties/vertex_groups/introduction.rst:11
msgid ""
"Vertex Groups are mainly used to tag the vertices belonging to parts of a Mesh "
"Object or :term:`Lattice`. Think of the legs of a chair or the hinges of a "
"door, or hands, arms, limbs, head, feet, etc. of a character. In addition you "
"can assign different *weight values* (in the range [ 0.0, 1.0 ] ) to the "
"vertices within a Vertex Group. Hence Vertex Groups are sometimes also named "
"*Weight Groups*."
msgstr ""
"顶点组主要被用来标记属于网格对象的顶点或者 :term:`晶格`。考虑椅子的腿和门的铰"
"链，或者手、胳膊、四肢、头、脚，一个字符等。此外你可以分配不同的 *权重* (范围在 "
"[ 0.0, 1.0 ] )给顶点组里的顶点。所以顶点组有时候被称作为 *权重组*。"

