msgid ""
"Many more usage scenarios are possible. Actually you can use Vertex Groups for "
"whatever makes sense to you. In some contexts Vertex Groups can also be "
"automatically generated (e.g. for rigged objects). However, in this section we "
"will focus on manually created (user-defined) Vertex Groups."
