#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/properties/vertex_groups/introduction.rst:45
msgid "Skinning an Armature"
msgstr "骨架蒙皮"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/properties/vertex_groups/introduction.rst:47
msgid ""
"If you want to animate your mesh and make it move, you will define an armature "
"which consists of a bunch of bones. Vertex Groups are used to associate parts "
"of the Mesh to Bones of the Armature, where you can specify an influence "
"*weight* in the range (0.0 - 1.0) for each vertex in the Vertex Group."
msgstr ""
"如果你想使你的网格有生命并且使它动起来，你可以定义一个由一堆骨骼组成的骨架。顶点"
"组可以被用来联系骨架的骨骼网格部分，你可以为每个顶点组里的顶点指定一个影响 *权重"
"* 在 (0.0 - 1.0) 范围里。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/properties/vertex_groups/introduction.rst:54
msgid ""
"Obviously, the same vertex can belong to several groups, and hence be affected "
"by several bones, with a fine tuning of each bone's influence using these "
"vertex weights. Quite useful when you want to have a smooth joint. For example, "
"when you skin an elbow, the upperarm vertex group contains the vertices of this "
"part at full weight (*1.0*), and when reaching the elbow area, these weights "
"decrease progressively to *0.0* when reaching the forearm zone and vice versa "
"for the forearm group weights... Of course, this is a very raw example skinning "
"a realistic joint is a big job, as you have to carefully find good weights for "
"each vertex, to have the most realistic behavior, when bending -- and this is "
"not an easy thing!"
msgstr ""
"明显的，同一个顶点可以属于好几个的组，因此可以被好几个骨骼影响，使用顶点权重微调"
"每个骨骼的影响。当你想要光滑的关节的时候，这个相当有用。比如说，当你覆盖肘关节的"
"时候，上臂顶点组包含这个部分满权重 (*1.0*)的顶点，并且到达肘关节附近，这些权重逐"
"步地减小到 *0.0* 当到达前臂区域，反过来也一样对前臂组权重....当然，这是一个非常"
"原始的例子，给一个真实的关节蒙皮是一个很大的任务，因为你必须很仔细地找到每个顶点"
"的好权重，当弯曲的时候使之拥有最真实的行为--它不是一件简单的事情！"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/properties/vertex_groups/introduction.rst:67
msgid ""
"Many modifiers contain the ability to control the modifier influence on each "
"vertex separately. This is also done via Vertex Groups and the weight values "
"associated to the vertices."
msgstr ""
"许多修改器包含控制每个分离的顶点修改造成的影响的功能。这个也被每一个顶点组用到并"
"且权重也和顶点相互联系。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/properties/vertex_groups/introduction.rst:74
msgid "Mesh Selection"
msgstr "网格选择"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/properties/vertex_groups/introduction.rst:76
msgid ""
"By defining mesh regions with Vertex Groups you can easily select entire parts "
"of your mesh with three clicks and work on them in isolation without having to "
"create separate objects. With the hide function you can even remove a vertex "
"group from the view (for later unhide)."
msgstr ""
"通过顶点组定义网格区域，你可以很简单地用三次点击选择整个网格并且分开地在上面工作"
"不需要创建分离的物体。通过隐藏的功能你甚至可以移除视图上的一个顶点组（接下来的取"
"消隐藏）。"
